snippet.title: The Big Picture - Uri Attacks: Diplomatic options & Challenges

localized.description:
Guests: Shashank, Former Foreign Secretary, Brig.(Retd) Rumel Dahiya, Deputy Director General, Institute of defence Studies and Analysis, Jayadev Ranade, Former Additional Secretary, Cabinet Secretariat, Manoj Joshi, Senior Fellow, Observer Research Foundation and on the phone line from Islamabad is Imtiaz Gul, Senior Journalist and Political analyst.

Anchor: Girish Nikam

Air Date: September 20, 2016
